[[圖瓦盧|圖瓦盧]]是西[[太平洋|太平洋]]的一個島國，位於[[澳大利亞|澳大利亞]]東北{{convert|4000|km|mi|sp=us}}，大致在澳大利亞和[[夏威夷群島|夏威夷群島]]之間。圖瓦盧西側是[[所羅門群島|所羅門群島]]，東南側是[[瑙魯|瑙魯]]，西側是[[托克勞|托克勞]]，西北側是[[薩摩亞|薩摩亞]]及[[瓦利斯和富圖納群島|瓦利斯和富圖納群島]]，北側是[[斐濟|斐濟]]。圖瓦盧國土面積非常小，僅有{{convert|26|km2|mi2|abbr=on}}，但其的[[專屬經濟區|專屬經濟區]]面積有{{convert|749790|km2|mi2|abbr=on}}，排名世界第38位。圖瓦盧包括三個堡礁，六個環礁<ref name="PSK1">{{cite journal| last = Paul S. Kench, Murray R. Ford & Susan D. Owen |title= Patterns of island change and persistence offer alternate adaptation pathways for atoll nations (Supplementary Note 1) | journal = Nature Communications| volume = 9| issue = 1| pages = 605|date = 9 February 2018| doi = 10.1038/s41467-018-02954-1| pmid = 29426825| pmc = 5807422| bibcode = 2018NatCo...9..605K}}</ref>。

圖瓦盧氣候可分為兩個季節。雨季是11月至4月，旱季是5月至10月<ref name=CFCT>{{cite web| title=Current and Future Climate of Tuvalu| work=[[Tuvalu_Meteorological_Service|Tuvalu Meteorological Service]], [[Australian_Bureau_of_Meteorology|Australian Bureau of Meteorology]] & [[Commonwealth_Scientific_and_Industrial_Research_Organisation|Commonwealth Scientific and Industrial Research Organisation]] (CSIRO)| date=2011| url=http://www.pacificclimatechangescience.org/wp-content/uploads/2013/06/4_PCCSP_Tuvalu_8pp.pdf| access-date=7 September 2015| archive-date=2021-01-19| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210119130203/https://www.pacificclimatechangescience.org/wp-content/uploads/2013/06/4_PCCSP_Tuvalu_8pp.pdf| dead-url=no}}</ref>。

